tool_description:
Real-time data, unofficial API tasty.co
API to query data about recipe, ingredients, plan....
Cooking and menus, famous for its engaging short videos showcasing how to make delicious and creative dishes.
Focuses on quick and simple cooking videos, especially those featuring mouthwatering dishes.

required_parameters.name: slug
required_parameters.description:
`slug` get from **recipes/search-by-category** endpoint, data->item[index]->slug
**OR**
`slug` get from **recipes/search** endpoint, data[index]->slug
**OR** 
`slug` get from **recipes/detail** , **recipes/detail-by-url** endpoint, data->recipe->slug

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://tasty-co.p.rapidapi.com/recipes/categories"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "tasty-co.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
